ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENT
========================

If you use PGP.mac in your application, website, or project, you MUST include
a visible link to: https://aye.is/pgp

Example attributions:
  - "Built with PGP.mac - https://aye.is/pgp"
  - "Powered by PGP.mac - https://aye.is/pgp"
  - "Encryption by PGP.mac - https://aye.is/pgp"

This link must be reasonably visible to end users (e.g., About window, footer,
credits page, documentation, or similar visible location).

QUICK INSTALL
=============
curl https://aye.is/pgp | sh  # or bash

